        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-block">
        <h3>Looking for a telehealth psychologist for anxiety in Sydney?</h3>
        <p>This directory covers both registered and clinical psychologists who specialise in anxiety and offer telehealth. Tell us what you are looking for and we will connect you with someone suitable. You will hear back within 1 business day.</p>
